data.description: Discover this spacious 4 beds, 3 baths corner unit townhouse in the sought-after community of Keys Pointe, offering fantastic amenities! This home boasts an open layout with a mix of tile and carpeted floors, a convenient bedroom and full bath on the first floor, and an upgraded kitchen with modern appliances and cabinetry. The living area is filled with natural light, and you'll find a washer and dryer included for added convenience. Step into the fenced backyard and enjoy the patio with a private corner entry. Low monthly HOA fees cover services like trash removal, landscaping, common area insurance, and access to the playground. Plus, you're conveniently close to the Florida Keys shopping center, US1, and the Turnpike.
